			FREQ
			Data block containing a set of frequencies in hertz (Hz.) It defines the frequency set for succeeding data within that data section which are functions of frequency.
			U.S. Geological Survey
			
			
			{frequencyMax}
			{frequencyMin}
			Hertz
		
		
		
		
